column1: # You can use comments if the first character of a line is # (care for spaces)
# Also empty lines are ignored (once again be careful not to have spaces)
# Don't place any commas or you might break it
# Place the names of the mods you want to enable here in the order you want them to be loaded in
# The name must be exactly as in the project.iml file of the mod
# The names can be copied from the "available_mods.csv" after running the program once
# which shows all inactive mods from your mods folder
# Bellow is an example of the mods I used have fun with the list if you want
Mafe Patch for Quest Generation Issues
Here Be Monsters: Koala's Creature Collection Compatibility Patch
Here Be Monsters: Void's HFLM Compatibility Patch
NKCC: The Festival of Light and Death
Quirk Expansion Pack by Marvin Seo
The Color of Blood and Venom
Here Be Monsters: Endless Harvest Waves
Here Be Monsters: The New Shadow
Koala's Creature Collection Monsters In Endless!
The Shrouded Chief: New Boss Mod
The Banshee by Marvin Seo and Clair de Lune
Marvin Seo's Color of Madness Trinkets
Sunward Isles: Marvin Seo Class Trinkets
